<br>
Squatting in Nejena killing level 9-15 mobs for days on end by yourself in the hopes that you get the 4 pages to drop is a far far far cry from what I would call &quot;epic&quot;.  There really isn't any story to speak of, either, attached to the magician epic.  Sure, there is the story of Magi'Kot and how he tried to master the Orb and failed and his essence is now trapped in the Orb but it doesn't compare to, say, the story behind the shaman epic which (if I understand correctly) follows the rise and fall of the City of Mist and actually provides some background and history to at least this small part of Norrath. <p>Dalynia Aziz<br>
